<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-1a' );" name="001-1a" class="pb">[001-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:198'>　陸氏易解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　　　明　姚士粦　輯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:223'>䷀乾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='223:231'>上九亢龍有悔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='231:242'>　陽極隂來吉去凶生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='242:252'>用九見羣龍无首吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='252:261'>　純陽用九之徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='261:287'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-1b' );" name="001-1b" class="pb">[001-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='287:293'>六位時成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='293:309'>　十二辰分六位升降以時消息吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='309:324'>利之<span class='krp-note'>今作/利物</span>足以和義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='324:333'>聖人作而萬物覩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='333:356'>　陽氣至五萬物茂盛故譬以聖人在天子之位功成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='356:367'>　制作萬物咸見之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='367:378'>六爻𤼵揮旁通情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='378:402'>　乾六爻𤼵揮變動旁通于坤坤來入乾以成六十四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='402:428'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-2a' );" name="001-2a" class="pb">[001-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='428:438'>　卦故曰旁通情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='438:442'>䷁坤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='442:454'>六三或從王事无成有終</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='454:477'>　隂臣陽君臣不敢為物之始陽唱隂和君命臣終其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='477:482'>　事也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='482:495'>上六龍戰于野其血𤣥黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='495:518'>　乾配西北積隂之地隂盛故戰乾坤伴處天地之氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='518:542'>　雜稱𤣥黃也又曰戌亥是乾之位乾伏本位積隂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='542:568'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-2b' );" name="001-2b" class="pb">[001-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='568:576'>　地猶盛故戰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='576:591'>為其嗛<span class='krp-note'>今作/嫌</span>于无陽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='591:603'>行<span class='krp-note'>今作/應</span>地无疆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='603:607'>䷂屯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='607:617'>雲雷屯君子以經綸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='617:640'>　水在雷上如雲雷交作天地草昧經綸之始无出于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='640:645'>　此也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='645:654'>初九盤桓利居貞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='654:680'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-3a' );" name="001-3a" class="pb">[001-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='680:693'>　屯難之際盤桓不進之貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='693:704'>女子貞不字十年乃字</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='704:719'>　字愛也時通則道亨合正匹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='719:723'>䷃蒙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='723:730'>匪我求童蒙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='730:749'>　六五隂爻在蒙暗蒙又體艮少故曰童蒙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='749:753'>䷄需</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='753:760'>六四需于血</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='760:786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-3b' );" name="001-3b" class="pb">[001-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='786:800'>　外卦坎水為險亦隂稱血也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='800:804'>䷅訟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='804:811'>天與水違行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='811:834'>　天道西行水東流其路背也外象乾西北方之卦内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='834:854'>　坎水正北方之卦其流東也二氣不交曰訟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='854:858'>䷆師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='858:867'>象曰地中有水師</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='867:891'>　坎在坤内故曰地中有水師衆也坤中衆者莫過于水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='891:917'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-4a' );" name="001-4a" class="pb">[001-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='917:925'>九二在師中吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='925:933'>　陽居九二也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='933:937'>䷇比</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='937:956'>　比卦一陽五隂少者為貴衆之所尊者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='956:961'>䷈小畜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='961:974'>宻雲不雨自我西郊尚往也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='974:988'>　一隂劣不能固陽是以往也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='988:992'>䷉履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='992:1018'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-4b' );" name="001-4b" class="pb">[001-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1018:1032'>剛中正履帝位而不疚光明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1032:1039'>　當履之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1039:1047'>眇能視跛能履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1047:1057'>　此履非其位六三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1057:1061'>䷊泰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1061:1069'>上六城復于隍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1069:1087'>　三陽務上坤順而往往而不巳否道至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1087:1091'>䷋否</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1091:1117'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-5a' );" name="001-5a" class="pb">[001-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1117:1127'>小人道長君子道消</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1127:1136'>　隂小人陽君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1136:1152'>其亡其亡繫于包<span class='krp-note'>今作/苞</span>桑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1152:1176'>　包本也言其堅固不亡如以巽繩繫也苞桑則叢桑也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1176:1186'>否終則傾何可長也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1186:1194'>　否極則泰來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1194:1199'>䷌同人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1199:1209'>九五先號咷而後笑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1209:1235'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-5b' );" name="001-5b" class="pb">[001-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1235:1258'>　隔于陽位不能决勝先克故曰號咷後獲合方喜故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1258:1264'>　曰後笑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1264:1269'>䷍大有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1269:1277'>火在天上大有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1277:1289'>　離為火為日故曰大有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1289:1297'>䷎謙<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1297:1301'>䷏豫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1301:1318'>天地以順動故日月不過而四時不忒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1318:1344'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-6a' );" name="001-6a" class="pb">[001-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1344:1351'>　坤順震動</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='1351:1355'>䷐隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='1355:1360'>動而說</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='1360:1376'>　震一陽二陰陽君隂民得其正也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='1376:1384'>王用亨于西山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='1384:1390'>　亨祭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='1390:1398'>䷑蠱<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='1398:1402'>䷒臨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='1402:1428'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-6b' );" name="001-6b" class="pb">[001-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='1428:1436'>至于八月有凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='1436:1449'>　建丑至未至于八月入遯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='1449:1453'>䷓觀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='1453:1459'>風行地上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='1459:1473'>　君子之徳風小人之徳草也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='1473:1480'>六三觀我生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='1480:1488'>　我生即道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='1488:1495'>利用賓于王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='1495:1521'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-7a' );" name="001-7a" class="pb">[001-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='1521:1532'>　臣道出于六四爻也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='1532:1537'>䷔噬嗑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='1537:1542'>動而明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='1542:1549'>　象雷電也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='1549:1572'>九四噬乾胏得金矢利艱貞吉象曰利艱貞吉未光也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='1572:1595'>　肉有骨謂之胏離為乾肉又為兵矢失位用刑物亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='1595:1618'>　不服若噬有骨之乾胏也金矢者取其剛直也噬胏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='1618:1640'>　雖復艱難終得申其剛直雖獲正吉未為光大也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='1640:1666'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-7b' );" name="001-7b" class="pb">[001-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='1666:1670'>䷕賁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='1670:1686'>六四賁如皤如白馬翰如匪冦婚媾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='1686:1709'>　震為馬為白故曰白馬翰如　按皤亦白素之貌也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='1709:1713'>䷖剥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='1713:1722'>象曰山附于地剥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='1722:1746'>　艮為山坤為地山附于地謂髙附于卑貴附于賤君不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='1746:1753'>　能制臣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='1753:1763'>君子得輿小人剝廬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='1763:1789'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-8a' );" name="001-8a" class="pb">[001-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='1789:1808'>　君子全得剥道安其位小人終不可安也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='1808:1812'>䷗復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='1812:1818'>七日來復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='1818:1841'>　七日陽之稱也七凡稱陽數也謂坤上六隂極陽戰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='1841:1864'>　之地隂雖不能勝陽然正當盛陽不可輕犯六陽涉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='1864:1883'>　六隂反下七爻在初故稱七日日亦陽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='1883:1899'>初九不逺復无禔<span class='krp-note'>今作/祗</span>悔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='1899:1916'>　反至初九陽來隂復逺違也禔安也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='1916:1942'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-8b' );" name="001-8b" class="pb">[001-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='1942:1951'>䷘无妄<span class='krp-note'>缺/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='1951:1956'>䷙大畜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='1956:1970'>六四童牛之角<span class='krp-note'>今作/牿</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='1970:1974'>䷚頥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='1974:1989'>天地養萬物聖人養賢以及萬民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='1989:1999'>　上下陽位包隂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='1999:2004'>䷛大過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='2004:2012'>大過大者過也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='2012:2038'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-9a' );" name="001-9a" class="pb">[001-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='2038:2045'>　大者相過</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='2045:2049'>䷜坎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='2049:2053'>習坎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='2053:2076'>　坎水龍深陷于物處坎之險不可不習故曰習坎便</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='2076:2099'>　習之習後不可履于險而不陷没者不以剛履柔不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='2099:2108'>　能成坎之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='2108:2118'>維心亨乃以剛中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='2118:2142'>　内外居坎陽處中而為坎主純隂得陽為名臣得君而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='2142:2168'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-9b' );" name="001-9b" class="pb">[001-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='2168:2184'>　安其居也君得一名臣而顯其道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='2184:2202'>象曰水洊至習坎君子以常徳行習教事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='2202:2225'>　洊再習重也水再至而益通流不舎晝夜重習相隨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='2225:2248'>　以為常有似于習故君子象之以常習教事如水不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='2248:2253'>　息也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='2253:2270'>六三來之坎坎險且枕入于坎窞勿用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='2270:2280'>　枕閑礙為害之貌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='2280:2284'>䷝離</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='2284:2311'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-10a' );" name="001-10a" class="pb">[001-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='2311:2326'>明兩作離大人以繼明照于四方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='2326:2349'>　離卦中虚始于乾象純剛健不能柔故以北方隂氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='2349:2359'>　貫中剛而文明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='2359:2363'>䷞咸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='2363:2372'>咸亨利貞取女吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='2372:2389'>　艮少男兊少女男下于女取婦之象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='2389:2399'>天地感而萬物化生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='2399:2418'>　天地因山澤孔竅以通其氣化生萬物也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='2418:2445'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-10b' );" name="001-10b" class="pb">[001-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='2445:2449'>䷟恒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='2449:2457'>九三不恒其徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='2457:2480'>　恒者常也而九三以陽居位立于隂陽交互之上是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='2480:2490'>　知不久為失所也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='2490:2494'>䷠遯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='2494:2501'>天下有山遯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='2501:2507'>　遯退也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='2507:2516'>遯之時義大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='2516:2543'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-11a' );" name="001-11a" class="pb">[001-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='2543:2562'>　謂陽氣退隂氣將害隨時遯避其義大矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='2562:2574'>初六遯尾厲勿用有攸往</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='2574:2597'>　隂氣已至于二而初在其後故曰遯尾也避難當在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='2597:2618'>　前而在後故厲往則與災難㑹故勿用有攸往</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='2618:2623'>䷡大壯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='2623:2637'>　内陽升降二衆俱陽曰大壯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='2637:2646'>君子以非禮弗履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='2646:2669'>　天尊雷卑君子見卑乘尊終必消除故象以為戒非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='2669:2696'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-11b' );" name="001-11b" class="pb">[001-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='2696:2702'>　禮不履</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='2702:2714'>喪羊于埸<span class='krp-note'>今作/易</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='2714:2722'>　埸謂疆埸也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='2722:2726'>䷢晉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='2726:2731'>晉康侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='2731:2739'>　康安也樂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='2739:2744'>䷣明夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='2744:2760'>六二明夷睇<span class='krp-note'>今作/夷</span>于左股</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='2760:2787'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-12a' );" name="001-12a" class="pb">[001-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='2787:2794'>　旁視曰睇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='2794:2799'>䷤家人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='2799:2808'>正家而天下定矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='2808:2831'>　聖人教先從家始家正則天下化之修已以安百姓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='2831:2836'>　者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='2836:2851'>婦子喜喜<span class='krp-note'>今作/嘻嘻</span>終吝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='2851:2862'>九五王假有家勿恤吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='2862:2885'>　假大也五得尊位據四應二以天下為家故曰王大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='2885:2912'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-12b' );" name="001-12b" class="pb">[001-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='2912:2927'>　有家天下正之故无所憂則吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='2927:2931'>䷥睽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='2931:2938'>說而麗乎明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='2938:2959'>　兊處下為積隂暗之象也離在上為明照于下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='2959:2978'>上九先張之弧後說之弧<span class='krp-note'>說合/作脫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='2978:2989'>　先疑暗也後說明也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='2989:2993'>䷦蹇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='2993:3010'>蹇當位貞吉以正國<span class='krp-note'>今作/邦</span>也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='3010:3037'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-13a' );" name="001-13a" class="pb">[001-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='3037:3046'>　正國為漢朝諱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='3046:3050'>䷧解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='3050:3056'>雷雨作解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='3056:3063'>　震雷坎雨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='3063:3078'>百果草木皆甲宅<span class='krp-note'>今作/拆</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='3078:3084'>　宅根也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='3084:3089'>解而拇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='3089:3096'>　拇足大指</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='3096:3123'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-13b' );" name="001-13b" class="pb">[001-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='3123:3127'>䷨損</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='3127:3133'>損下益上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='3133:3152'>　乾九三變六三隂柔益上九臣奉君之象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='3152:3167'>君子以懲忿□<span class='krp-note'>今作/窒</span>欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='3167:3171'>䷩益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='3171:3176'>風雷益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='3176:3194'>　内外順動風雷益四象分明剛柔定矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='3194:3198'>䷪夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='3198:3225'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-14a' );" name="001-14a" class="pb">[001-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='3225:3234'>象曰澤上于天夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='3234:3248'>　水氣上天决降成雨故曰夬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='3248:3252'>䷫姤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='3252:3266'>天下有風姤后以號令誥四方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='3266:3288'>　巽入也風入于坤皆動也故知天下有動其物也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='3288:3297'>姤之時義大矣哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='3297:3312'>　天地相遇萬物亦然其義大矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='3312:3325'>累<span class='krp-note'>今作/羸</span>豕孚蹢躅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='3325:3352'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-14b' );" name="001-14b" class="pb">[001-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='3352:3356'>䷬萃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='3356:3371'>萃王假有廟<span class='krp-note'>萃下无/亨字</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='3371:3394'>　王五廟上也王者聚百物以祭其先諸侯助祭于廟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='3394:3407'>　中假大也言五親奉上矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='3407:3425'>象曰澤上于地萃君子以除戎器戒不虞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='3425:3448'>　除猶脩治也凡聚衆必慎防閑暇陽為主成萃之義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='3448:3461'>　伏戎必豫備衆聚去疑心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='3461:3465'>䷭升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='3465:3492'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-15a' );" name="001-15a" class="pb">[001-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='3492:3509'>地中生木升君子以順徳積小以髙大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='3509:3520'>　合抱之木始于毫末</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='3520:3544'>王用亨于岐山<span class='krp-note'>亨嘆音火庚反今/此作祭享之享</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='3544:3548'>䷮困</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='3548:3571'>　困卦上下不應隂陽不交六三隂上六亦隂无配入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='3571:3583'>　九五求陽陽亦无納也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='3583:3589'>九五劓刖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='3589:3598'>　劓刖當為倪㐳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='3598:3625'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-15b' );" name="001-15b" class="pb">[001-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='3625:3635'>象曰劓刖志未得也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='3635:3658'>　无據无應故志未得也二言朱紱此言赤紱二言享</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='3658:3681'>　祀此言祭祀傳互言耳无他義也謂二困五三困四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='3681:3695'>　五初困上斯乃迭困之義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='3695:3699'>䷯井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='3699:3707'>井改邑不改井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='3707:3728'>　井道以澄清見用為功也井象徳不可渝變也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='3728:3742'>木上有水井君子以勞民勸相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='3742:3769'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-16a' );" name="001-16a" class="pb">[001-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='3769:3785'>　井以徳立君正民信徳以其道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='3785:3791'>井收勿幕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='3791:3798'>　收井幹也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='3798:3802'>䷰革</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='3802:3809'>革已日乃孚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='3809:3816'>　孚猶信也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='3816:3828'>象曰君子豹變其文蔚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='3828:3851'>　兊之陽爻稱虎隂爻稱豹豹虎類而小者也君子小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='3851:3878'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-16b' );" name="001-16b" class="pb">[001-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='3878:3892'>　于大人故曰豹變其文蔚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='3892:3896'>䷱鼎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='3896:3908'>鼎象也以木巽火亨飪也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='3908:3932'>　木見火中𤼵火木相資象鼎之兆下穴為足中虚見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='3932:3941'>　納飪熟之義明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='3941:3948'>九三鼎耳革</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='3948:3957'>　九三成鼎之徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='3957:3974'>六五鼎黄耳象曰鼎黄耳中以為實也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='3974:4001'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-17a' );" name="001-17a" class="pb">[001-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='4001:4024'>　六五委任賢臣假之位也得中承陽故曰中以為實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='4024:4028'>䷲震</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='4028:4034'>震驚百里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='4034:4058'>　震為雷聲驚于百里春𤼵秋收順天行也取象定吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='4058:4062'>　凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='4062:4070'>䷳艮<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='4070:4074'>䷴漸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='4074:4091'>漸之進也女歸吉也進得位往有功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='4091:4118'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-17b' );" name="001-17b" class="pb">[001-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='4118:4141'>　艮變八卦終于漸漸終降純隂入坤分長女三隂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='4141:4150'>　兆也柔道行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='4150:4158'>初六鴻漸于干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='4158:4165'>　水畔稱干</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='4165:4177'>六二鴻漸于磐飲食衎衎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='4177:4185'>　賢人進位也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='4185:4197'>六四鴻漸于木或得其桷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='4197:4203'>　桷榱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='4203:4230'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-18a' );" name="001-18a" class="pb">[001-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='4230:4235'>䷵歸妹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='4235:4241'>歸妹征凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='4241:4259'>　震長男兊少女少女匹長男氣非合也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='4259:4271'>歸妹以嬬<span class='krp-note'>今作/須</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='4271:4277'>　嬬妾也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='4277:4281'>䷶豐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='4281:4301'>豐其屋蔀其家闚其户闃其无人三嵗不覿凶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='4301:4320'>　上六積暗而動凶之于上反下見隂之兆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='4320:4347'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-18b' );" name="001-18b" class="pb">[001-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='4347:4351'>䷷旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='4351:4358'>山上有火旅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='4358:4370'>　火在上无止象旅之義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='4370:4382'>初六旅瑣瑣斯其所取災</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='4382:4405'>　瑣瑣小也艮為小石故曰旅瑣瑣也履非其正應離</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='4405:4428'>　之始離為火艮為山以應火災焚自取也故曰斯其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='4428:4435'>　所取災也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='4435:4439'>䷸巽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='4439:4466'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-19a' );" name="001-19a" class="pb">[001-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='4466:4481'>　木乾象陰來盪成巽巽者順也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='4481:4490'>象曰重巽以申命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='4490:4505'>　巽為命令重命令者欲丁寧也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='4505:4515'>剛巽乎中正而志行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='4515:4538'>　二得中五得正體兩巽故曰剛巽乎中正也皆據隂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='4538:4545'>　故志行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='4545:4556'>柔皆順乎剛是以小亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='4556:4566'>　隂為卦主故小亨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='4566:4593'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-19b' );" name="001-19b" class="pb">[001-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='4593:4597'>䷹兊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='4597:4604'>兊說以先民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='4604:4625'>　兊下六隂凝艮上于陽健納兊為妻二氣合也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='4625:4629'>䷺渙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='4629:4635'>　渙散也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='4635:4642'>乘木有功也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='4642:4649'>　虚舟行也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='4649:4655'>風行水上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='4655:4682'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-20a' );" name="001-20a" class="pb">[001-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='4682:4690'>　木浮于水也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='4690:4698'>䷻節<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='4698:4703'>䷼中孚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='4703:4710'>　中孚信也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='4710:4720'>豚魚吉信及豚魚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='4720:4738'>　豚魚幽微之物信尚及之何况于人乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='4738:4755'>我有好爵吾與爾䌕<span class='krp-note'>今作/縻</span>之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='4755:4764'>䷽小過<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='4764:4791'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-20b' );" name="001-20b" class="pb">[001-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='4791:4796'>䷾既濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='4796:4821'>　坎離分子午水上火下性相交敵不相間隔故曰既濟也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='4821:4826'>䷿未濟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='4826:4844'>　離炎上坎務下二象不合各殊隂陽也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='4844:4848'>繫辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='4848:4855'>鼓之以雷霆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='4855:4862'>　鼔鼔動也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='4862:4873'>六爻之動三極之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='4873:4900'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-21a' );" name="001-21a" class="pb">[001-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='4900:4923'>　極至也天有隂陽二氣地有剛柔二性人有仁義二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='4923:4946'>　行六爻之動法乎此也凡三才極至之道也初四下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='4946:4959'>　極二五中極三上上極也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='4959:4974'>是故君子所居而安者易之序也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='4974:4980'>　序象也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='4980:4989'>辯吉凶者存乎辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='4989:5000'>　吉凶之兆見乎爻象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='5000:5014'>夫乾其静也顓<span class='krp-note'>今作/專</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='5014:5041'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-21b' );" name="001-21b" class="pb">[001-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='5041:5064'>子曰勞而不伐有功而不置<span class='krp-note'>今作/徳</span>厚之至也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='5064:5077'>野容誨淫<span class='krp-note'>野今/作冶</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='5077:5091'>　野言妖野容儀教誨淫佚也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='5091:5103'>凡三百有六十當期之日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='5103:5126'>　日月十二交㑹積三百五十四日有竒為一㑹今云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='5126:5149'>　三百六十當期則入十三月六日也十三月為一期</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='5149:5159'>　故云當期之日也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='5159:5168'>是故四營而成易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='5168:5195'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-22a' );" name="001-22a" class="pb">[001-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='5195:5218'>　分而為二以象兩一營也掛一以象三二營也揲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='5218:5241'>　以四以象四時三營也歸竒于扐以象閏四營也謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='5241:5256'>　四度營為方成易之一爻者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='5256:5264'>以動者尚其變</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='5264:5280'>　變為爻之變化當議之而後動矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='5280:5288'>夫易開物成務</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='5288:5311'>　開物謂庖犧引伸八卦重以為六十四觸長爻策至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='5311:5334'>　于萬一千五百二十以當萬物之數故曰開物聖人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='5334:5361'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-22b' );" name="001-22b" class="pb">[001-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='5361:5384'>　觀象而制網罟耒耜之屬以成天下之務故曰成務</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='5384:5388'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='5388:5403'>六爻之義易以工<span class='krp-note'>今作/貢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='5403:5409'>退藏于宻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='5409:5426'>　受蓍龜之報應决而退藏之于心也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='5426:5436'>是興神物以前民用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='5436:5459'>　神物蓍也聖人興蓍以别吉凶先民而用之民皆從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='5459:5470'>　焉故曰以前民用也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='5470:5497'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-23a' );" name="001-23a" class="pb">[001-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='5497:5505'>以神明其徳夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='5505:5528'>　聖人以蓍能逆知吉凶除害就利清潔其身故曰以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='5528:5551'>　此齋戒也吉而後行舉不違失其徳富盛見稱神明</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='5551:5561'>　故曰神明其徳也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='5561:5574'>利用出入民咸用之謂之神</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='5574:5597'>　聖人制器以周民用用之不遺故曰利用出入也民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='5597:5614'>　皆用之而不知所由來故謂之神也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='5614:5624'>天地變化聖人效之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='5624:5651'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-23b' );" name="001-23b" class="pb">[001-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='5651:5674'>　天有晝夜四時變化之道聖人設三百八十四爻以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='5674:5680'>　效之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='5680:5689'>變而通之以盡利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='5689:5709'>　變三百八十四爻使相交通以盡天下之利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='5709:5723'>舉而措之天下之民謂之事業</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='5723:5746'>　變通盡利觀象制器舉而措之于天下民咸用之以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='5746:5752'>　為事業</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='5752:5768'>擬諸其形容象其物宜是故謂之象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l421' data-llen='5768:5795'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-24a' );" name="001-24a" class="pb">[001-24a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l422' data-llen='5795:5813'>　此明說立象盡意設卦盡情偽之意也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l423' data-llen='5813:5824'>極天下之賾者存乎卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l424' data-llen='5824:5838'>　言卦象極盡天下之深情也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l425' data-llen='5838:5848'>天地之道貞觀者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l426' data-llen='5848:5862'>　言天地正可以觀瞻為道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l427' data-llen='5862:5872'>日月之道貞明者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l428' data-llen='5872:5885'>　言日月正以明照為道矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l429' data-llen='5885:5901'>夫坤妥<span class='krp-note'>今作/隤</span>然示人簡矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l430' data-llen='5901:5928'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-24b' );" name="001-24b" class="pb">[001-24b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l431' data-llen='5928:5936'>何以聚人曰財</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l432' data-llen='5936:5959'>　人非財不聚故聖人觀象制器備物盡利以業萬民</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l433' data-llen='5959:5973'>　而聚之也葢取聚人之本矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l434' data-llen='5973:5980'>觀鳥獸之文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l435' data-llen='5980:6003'>　謂朱鳥白虎蒼龍𤣥武四方二十八宿經緯之文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l436' data-llen='6003:6009'>斵木為耜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l437' data-llen='6009:6020'>　耜耒下耓也廣五寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l438' data-llen='6020:6042'>易窮則變變則通通則久是以自天祐之吉无不利</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l439' data-llen='6042:6069'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-25a' );" name="001-25a" class="pb">[001-25a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l440' data-llen='6069:6092'>　隂窮則變為陽陽窮則變為隂天之道也庖犧作網</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l441' data-llen='6092:6115'>　罟教民取禽獸以充民食民衆獸少其道窮則神農</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l442' data-llen='6115:6138'>　教布殖以變之此窮變之大要也窮則變變則通與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l443' data-llen='6138:6157'>　天終始故可久民得其用故无所不利也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l444' data-llen='6157:6173'>既辱且危死期將至妻其可得見邪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l445' data-llen='6173:6196'>　六三從困辱之象易之大過為棺槨死䘮之象故曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l446' data-llen='6196:6209'>　死期將至妻不可得見也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l447' data-llen='6209:6218'>道有變動故曰爻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l448' data-llen='6218:6245'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-25b' );" name="001-25b" class="pb">[001-25b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l449' data-llen='6245:6268'>　天道有晝夜日月之變地道有剛柔燥濕之變人道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l450' data-llen='6268:6291'>　有行止動静吉凶善惡之變聖人設爻以效三者之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l451' data-llen='6291:6302'>　變動故謂之爻者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l452' data-llen='6302:6308'>危者使平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l453' data-llen='6308:6331'>　文王在紂世有危亡之患故于易辭多趨危亡求自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l454' data-llen='6331:6354'>　免濟建成王業故易爻辭危者使平以象其事否卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l455' data-llen='6354:6371'>　九五其亡其亡繫于苞桑之屬是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l456' data-llen='6371:6377'>易者使傾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l457' data-llen='6377:6404'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-26a' );" name="001-26a" class="pb">[001-26a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l458' data-llen='6404:6427'>　易平易也紂安其位自謂平易而反傾覆故易爻辭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l459' data-llen='6427:6450'>　易者使傾以象其事明夷上六初登于天後入于地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l460' data-llen='6450:6457'>　之屬是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l461' data-llen='6457:6464'>水火不相射</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l462' data-llen='6464:6472'>　射音亦厭也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l463' data-llen='6472:6478'>帝出乎震</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l464' data-llen='6478:6489'>　安為動主静為躁君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l465' data-llen='6489:6498'>乾為首為君為父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l466' data-llen='6498:6525'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-26b' );" name="001-26b" class="pb">[001-26b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l467' data-llen='6525:6544'>　乾為首也乾象堅剛天地之尊故為君父</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l468' data-llen='6544:6551'>坤為腹為母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l469' data-llen='6551:6559'>　坤順容于物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l470' data-llen='6559:6566'>乾為馬為龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l471' data-llen='6566:6575'>　天行運轉不息</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l472' data-llen='6575:6580'>為阪生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l473' data-llen='6580:6587'>　阪當作反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l474' data-llen='6587:6591'>爲風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l475' data-llen='6591:6618'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-27a' );" name="001-27a" class="pb">[001-27a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l476' data-llen='6618:6641'>　風土氣也巽坤之所生故為風亦取静於本而動於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l477' data-llen='6641:6646'>　末也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l478' data-llen='6646:6661'>爲矯輮<span class='krp-note'>漢讀為扭/挼二音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l479' data-llen='6661:6668'>　輮讀為柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l480' data-llen='6668:6673'>為小石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l481' data-llen='6673:6687'>　艮剛卦之小故為小石者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l482' data-llen='6687:6703'>訟必有衆起故受之以師師者衆也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l483' data-llen='6703:6726'>　丈人者聖人也帥師未必聖人若漢髙祖光武應此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l484' data-llen='6726:6753'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0005', 'WYG', '001-27b' );" name="001-27b" class="pb">[001-27b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l485' data-llen='6753:6758'>　義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l486' data-llen='6758:6764'>明夷誅也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l487' data-llen='6764:6770'>　誅傷也</span><br/>
